# `callEdgeFunction`

All Edge Function calls from the app go through `src/lib/api.ts`:

- `createClient()` from `@/lib/supabase/client`
- `getSession()` → require `access_token`
- `POST` to `${NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL}/functions/v1/${name}`
- Headers: `Content-Type: application/json`, `Authorization: Bearer <token>`, `apikey: NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`
- Parse JSON; if `!res.ok` or `data.error`, throw with message

Do not duplicate this fetch logic elsewhere — import and use `callEdgeFunction`.
